<item>
            <title>[SEC-2701] DaoAuthenticationProvider shadows actual authentication exceptions</title>
                <link>https://jira.spring.io/browse/SEC-2701</link>
                <project id="10040" key="SEC">Spring Security</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Hi, it seems that DaoAuthenticationProvider#retrieveUser semantics  have changed since 3.0.x.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Indeed, DaoAuthenticationProvider was catching only some particular exceptions back then, thus propagating the other ones possibly thrown by the configured UserDetailsService.&lt;/p&gt;

